jparsec.time.calendar

Class Calendar

  • java.lang.Object
    • jparsec.time.calendar.Calendar

  • public class Calendar
extends java.lang.Object
    A support class for the calendars, based on Calendrical Calculations book.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    T. Alonso Albi - OAN (Spain)
